c. 下单成功页面（Order Confirmation Page）
在客户下单成功后显示以下文字：
“Order Confirmed! 🎉 Thank you so much for your order.
Since this is a customized cake, please reach out to us on Instagram or via
email to share your design photo and details.
Instagram: @lumii
_paws
Email: lumiipaws0206@gmail.com”
如果订单里没有定制蛋糕（只有零食），就不要显示这段话。
d. 订单确认邮件（Order Confirmation Email）


{% comment %}Show callout only if the order includes a customized cake{% endcomment %}
{% assign has_custom_cake = false %}
{% for line_item in checkout.line_items %}
  {% if line_item.product %}
    {% assign tags_string = line_item.product.tags | join: ',' | downcase %}
    {% assign product_type = line_item.product.type | downcase %}
    {% if tags_string contains 'custom-cake' or product_type contains 'custom cake' %}
      {% assign has_custom_cake = true %}
      {% break %}
    {% endif %}
  {% endif %}
{% endfor %}

{% if has_custom_cake %}
  <div class="order-confirmation-message" style="margin:16px 0;padding:16px;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;border-radius:8px;background:#f9fafb;">
    <p style="margin:0;">
      Order Confirmed! 🎉 Thank you so much for your order.<br>
      Since this is a customized cake, please reach out to us on Instagram or via email to share your design photo and details.<br>
      Instagram: @lumii_paws<br>
      Email: <a href="mailto:lumiipaws0206@gmail.com">lumiipaws0206@gmail.com</a>
    </p>
  </div>
{% endif %}